## Expand FHIR unit-test coverage

### Context
The existing `TestFhirImportService` covered the pre-version-selection surface.
After adding multi-version support the new code paths had no tests.

### Changes
1. `tests/units/ontology/test_industry_importers.py`
   - **Version catalog** — `get_fhir_versions()` shape, required fields, R4/R4B/R5
     presence, exactly-one-default invariant.
   - **URL routing** — `_fetch_fhir_ttl(version)` calls the correct HL7 base URL
     for each of R4, R4B, R5; unknown version raises `ValidationError`.
   - **`ontology_info` propagation** — `_transform_fhir_to_ontobricks` embeds the
     version string in `version`, `name`, and `description` fields; description
     contains the matching base URL.
