## Fix: ontology assistant crash on first invocation — PITFALL_RULES.md excluded from deploy

### Context
The ontology assistant endpoint (`POST /ontology/assistant/chat`) raised a `FileNotFoundError`
at module-import time because `PITFALL_RULES.md` was never synced to the Databricks App.
The `*.md` exclusion rule in `databricks.yml` was too broad: it swept up runtime-required
data files alongside documentation.

### Changes
1. `databricks.yml` — added `src/agents/PITFALL_RULES.md` to `sync.include` so the DAB
   deploy uploads it even though `*.md` is globally excluded.

### Modified files
- `databricks.yml`

### Tests
No test change needed — the fix is in the deploy config.

---

## Fix: ontology assistant FAB requires two clicks to open on fresh page load

### Context
On first load, the popup visibility is driven by CSS (`.assistant-popup { display: none }`).
`popup.style.display` returns `""` (no inline style), so `"" !== "none"` evaluated to `true`
— the first click treated the popup as visible and hid it; the second click opened it.

### Changes
1. `src/front/static/ontology/js/ontology-assistant.js` line 50 — switched
   `popup.style.display` to `getComputedStyle(popup).display` so the check reflects
   the actual rendered state regardless of whether the value comes from CSS or an
   inline style.

### Modified files
- `src/front/static/ontology/js/ontology-assistant.js`

### Tests
Manual verification: single click now opens the popup on fresh page load.

---

## Fix: PITFALL_RULES.md not synced by DAB — renamed to .txt

### Context
The `databricks.yml` `sync.include` override for `PITFALL_RULES.md` did not reliably
override the `*.md` glob exclusion. Renamed the file to `PITFALL_RULES.txt` so it
never matches the exclusion pattern, eliminating the need for any special include entry.

### Changes
1. `src/agents/PITFALL_RULES.md` → deleted
2. `src/agents/PITFALL_RULES.txt` → new (same content)
3. `src/agents/agent_ontology_assistant/engine.py` — `_PITFALL_RULES_PATH` updated to `.txt`
4. `databricks.yml` — removed the now-unnecessary `src/agents/PITFALL_RULES.md` include entry

Deployed successfully via `make deploy`.

### Modified files
- `src/agents/PITFALL_RULES.txt` (renamed from .md)
- `src/agents/agent_ontology_assistant/engine.py`
- `databricks.yml`

### Tests
